TI  == isolation of porphyromonas gingivalis strain from tubal-ovarian abscess.
AB  == an unusual case of involvement of porphyromonas gingivalis is described. two anaerobic isolates, identified as fusobacterium nucleatum and p. gingivalis, were recovered from the pus of a tubal-ovarian abscess in a 35-year-old woman. identification of the p. gingivalis isolate was confirmed by randomly amplified polymorphic dna fingerprinting.
